query:
SELECT COUNT(*) as registros_faltantes
FROM planes_sustitucion ps
WHERE ps.puestoClave = 'Si' 
  AND ps.id NOT IN (SELECT COALESCE(planSustitucionId, 0) FROM planes_sucesion)
